high_descs: Go to the right side of the round black table that is ahead.
Take the yellow handle knife from the table.
Turn around, go to the black stand to the left of the white table.
Cut the potato on the stand into slices.
Turn right, go straight and to the right to the oven.
Put the knife in the microwave above the oven.
Turn around, bear right across the room back to the black stand.
Take a slice of potato from the stand.
Turn right, go straight and to the right to the oven.
Cook the slice of potato in the microwave. Take the slice of potato from the microwave.
Turn around, bear right across the room back to the black stand.
Put the slice of potato on the lower right corner of the black stand.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of potato on a stand.

high_descs: Go to the right and walk towards the round black table in the corner.
Pick up the knife next to the tomato on the table.
Turn around and walk straight to the black shelf in the corner beside the white table.
Cut the potato on the shelf to a couple of slices.
Turn around and go to the left towards the microwave oven on top of the stove.
Open the microwave oven, put the knife inside and close the microwave.
Turn around and walk straight back to the black shelf again.
Pick up a slice of the potato from the shelf.
Turn around and go to the left towards the microwave oven again.
Open the microwave, put the slice of potato inside, close the microwave and heat it for a few seconds, after that open the microwave and grab the potato.
Turn around and walk straight to the black shelf again.
Put the slice of potato next to the loaf of bread on the black shelf
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of potato on the black shelf.

high_descs: Turn right, turn left, walk towards the black round counter
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle
Turn left, turn left towards the black table
walk straight to the small black table with a bread box
Turn right, walk straight towards the oven with a microwave on top
Open the microwave, put the knife inside
Turn left, turn left, walk straight, turn right towards the small black table
Pick up a slice of a cut apple
Turn right, turn right, walk straight towards the oven with a microwave
Open the microwave, put the apple inside, set the timer, open the microwave
Take the apple, turn left, turn left, walk straight, turn right towards the small black table
Place the slice of apple on the small black table
anns.task_desc: Cook an apple inside the microwave and set it on the black table
